                     <interp inst="t18330103-48-off281" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18330103-48-cd282" type="crimeDate">4th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18330103-48-off281 t18330103-48-cd282"></join>, at St. Marylebone, 1 purse, value 1s., and 10 sovereigns, the property of 
                     
